    "body": "Problem:  Invalidated regions that are flushed during startup are\r\n          cleared with unitialized \"clear_attrs\", which is perceived as\r\n          flickering.\r\nSolution: Initialize \"clear_attrs\" with current terminal background color.\r\n\r\nFix #28667",
